      • perform

        public void perform(List<String> wordList_previous,
                    int iteration_counter,
                    String example_dir,
                    String domain,
                    List<Boolean> enginechoice,
                    List<String> queries,
                    int results_number,
                    int top_visible,
                    List<Boolean> mozMetrics,
                    boolean moz_threshold_option,
                    double moz_threshold,
                    int top_count_moz,
                    List<Boolean> ContentSemantics,
                    int SensebotConcepts,
                    List<Double> LSHrankSettings,
                    String config_path)
        Method to call search analysis for every query and to save the wordlists
        Parameters:
        wordList_previous - the previous wordlist to check convergence
        iteration_counter - the iteration number
        example_dir - the directory to save the files
        domain - the domain we analyze
        enginechoice - the search engines chosen
        queries - the queries we search for
        results_number - the amount of results for each query
        top_visible - the amount of results if we use Visibility Score (http://www.advancedwebranking.com/user-guide/html/en/ch08s06.html)
        mozMetrics - the metrics of Moz chosen
        moz_threshold_option - flag if we are going to use Moz threshold or not
        moz_threshold - the threshold to moz metrics
        top_count_moz - the amount of links to keep if we use Moz for evaluation
        ContentSemantics - get the choice of Content Semantic Analysis algorithm that we are going to use
        SensebotConcepts - the amount of concepts to be recognized if Sensebot is used
        LSHrankSettings - the settings for LDA and LSHrank in general (check the ReadInput Class)
        config_path - the configuration path to get all the api keys
